<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM8.3">
<l>oḷivaṇṇam vaḷaicintai uṟakkattō ṭivaiyellām</l>
<l>eḷimaiyā liṭṭeṉṉai yīṭaḻiyap pōyiṉavāl</l>
<l>kuḷiraruvi vēṅkaṭatteṉ kōvintaṉ kuṇampāṭi</l>
<l>aḷiyatta mēkaṅkā ḷāvikāt tiruppēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] lustre, colour, bracelets, thoughts, all these along with sleep</l>
<l>have left, forsaking [me] due to [my] weakness, so that I am fully destroyed, alas!</l>
<l>O graceful clouds! Will I stay alive singing the qualities of</l>
<l>my Govinda from Veṅkaṭam with cool waterfalls!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
